#: of numpy.ma.core.asarray:10
msgid ""
"Input data, in any form that can be converted to a masked array. This "
"includes lists, lists of tuples, tuples, tuples of tuples, tuples of lists, "
"ndarrays and masked arrays."
msgstr ""

